      label: "Leadership Framework",
      hoverSummary: 'FTDA is Lance Fisher\'s operational playbook for technical team leadership, built from 15+ years leading cross-functional teams in live operations at Microsoft. It covers onboarding architecture, shift expectations, performance culture, documentation standards, mentorship pipelines, cross-site development, and the systems that turn good teams into great ones. Every principle was designed intentionally, tested in production, and refined through repeated onboarding cycles with measurable results. This is not theory. This is how B-Side Overnight was rebuilt from the ground up.',
      thumbnail: { type: "canvas", src: "" },
